body: Looking at the pr that introduced this method, https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/pull/5781, it looks like it was not documented at the time. I believe one thing that needs to happen is to add a docstring for the method in `_torch_docs.py`. I would be happy to send a PR for it, unless there's some reason it should not have a docstring.
